[00. simple print
hello world
01. severity
info: one
emerg: two
mode was: 0x0001
02. suppress severity
info: this message is seen
emerg: and this one as well
03. suppress severity name
info: this message is seen
emerg: and this one as well
04. severity mask
one
two
emerg: three
05. locus: file, line
input:1: file, line
06. locus: file, line, col
input:1.1-10: file, line, col
07. locus: file, line-range
