input:1.8-next:2.10: locus column changed
13. advance locus column
input:1.1-next:5.10: initial
input:1.5-next:5.10: locus line advanced
14. fmt: severity
info: severity
15. fmt: locus (file, line)
a:10: one
16. fmt: locus (file, line, column)
a:10.5: one
17. fmt: locus (range)
